Send Feedback SUBMIT RATING Device Info Feedback Version: Device Info is an application which queries data from android device and obtain HW features which are normally not available through user interface. It contains several modules visible from main menu. Device Info application also offers a possibility to test GPS and network using ping command.\n\nGoogle Play and the Google Play logo are trademarks of Google LLC. © Device Info by pacmac 2020. If you like using this app, would you mind taking a moment to rate it? It won\'t take more than a minute. Thank you for your support! Camera permission is currently disabled. To be able to obtain camera parameters you need to accept camera permission. Read phone state permission is currently disabled. To be able to access SIM and mobile network status you need to accept this permission. You can revoke permission anytime from phone Settings. Location permission is required in order to display information about mobile network environment. Storage permission is currently disabled. To be able to read storage capacity you need to accept this permission.
What is new - GNSS Hardware Year: Added Global Navigation Satellite System year of hardware into main GPS view for phones running Anroid P and newer. - Android 11(R) Preview Support: Added support for Android 11(R) Preview version. - Several Crash Fixes Cellular Info
